# VHS Tape: kapi overview demo
# Quick overview of kapi CLI capabilities

Output output/overview.webm
Output output/overview.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20

Type "kapi --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# List supported formats"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "kapi formats"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# List available tools"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "kapi tools"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Sleep 1s
